Panel B-SenMayo Enrichment Scores: Child vs Young Adult

SenMayo enrichment scores were calculated using Gene Set Enrichment Analysis (GSEA) to evaluate senescence-associated transcriptional programs across major lung cell populations.

Workflow:

Gene expression signatures were obtained from the integrated pediatric lung snRNA-seq dataset.
SenMayo gene signatures were analyzed using GSEA.
Normalized enrichment scores (NES) were calculated for each cell population.
Child and Young Adult groups were compared.
Results were visualized using GraphPad Prism.

